{"tid":1606594,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一條好認真嘅問題","createTime":"2019-09-30T15:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:42:01.000Z","uid":201712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92073ae0f0d451dfdbb4057f22ad7700842573cb","tid":1606594,"uid":201712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:16:27.000Z","msg":"如果有一樣野 你當下好想同你另外一半講<br />\n但係其實俾唔到你任何好處 只不過係發洩一下<br />\n仲會導致鬧交 或者唔開心<br />\n佢唔一定會反省<br />\n咁你會唔會講出嚟？<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻 <br />\n如果你另一半成日話屋企唔俾出夜街 或者過夜<br />\n但係佢有時就會同D friend出夜街玩 或者過夜玩<br />\n<br />\n咁你會唔會話一話佢？ 假設當下妳好想話佢<br />\n但係後果只會導致大家唔開心<br />\n咁你仲會唔會咁做？ <br />\n<br />\n定係等到下次想同佢出夜街 或者過夜嘅時候先講<br />\n但係嗰陣嘅效果一定冇咁顯著"},{"pid":"88d3d36320895fb1733c1bf839816246b2062540","tid":1606594,"uid":201712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78ed52987ed3ac050a4389419da9ebc0e1daa02","tid":1606594,"uid":201712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94092e48706d3319b12cc343b21d2123c005c68","tid":1606594,"uid":220603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:18:05.000Z","msg":"我了 硬"},{"pid":"38ca71eebd5cd9b74ac408542ac0acf8f42e7d20","tid":1606594,"uid":201712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7825327fdb7dae44f292b3fd87af79a3de079f9","tid":1606594,"uid":201712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:20:51.000Z","msg":"想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos